---
title: Mexican Spiced Veggie Bowl with Beyond Meat® and Mexican-Style Red Rice
description: A deconstructed burrito? Yes, please! There's no need for the tortilla when Beyond Meat® teams up with hearty Mexican-spiced basmati rice, crispy pan-seared peppers, fresh tomatoes and a citrusy lime crema.
